<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 zài shì jiè de dōng fāng yǒu yī gè guó jiā,
 zài zhè gè xīng qiú shàng yǒu yī gè guó jiā,
 tā jiù shì wǒ zuì qīn ài de zǔ guó, míng zì jiào zhōng huá.
 tā yì lì zài shì jiè de dōng fāng, míng zì jiào zhōng huá.
 shàng xià wǔ qiān nián, jīng shòu duō shǎo fēng chuī yǔ dǎ,
 fù lǎo xiāng qīn men, qín láo shàn liáng pǔ shí wú huá.
 hěn duō hěn duō de dì xiōng jiě mèi, shēn shēn bǎ tā qiān guà.
 cóng zǎo dào wǎn mò mò gēng yún, wèi zhōng huá tiān zhuān jiā wǎ.
 wǒ jīn tiān yào chàng yī zhī gē, ràng gē shēng chuán biàn tiān yá.
 wǒ jīn tiān yào wèi nǐ qí dǎo, qīn ài de zhōng huá.
 gào sù sì hǎi de qīn rén péng yǒu, wèi zhōng huá zhù fú ba.
 yuàn zhè zhēn chéng de qí dǎo, huà zuò yī duǒ duǒ bǎi hé huā.
 chūn fēng yǐ jīng chuī kāi le, zhè yī piàn gǔ lǎo de jiāng tǔ.
 kāi biàn nǐ de měi yī chù yuán yě, měi yī zuò shān yá.
 zhè lǐ shì yī gè fù xìng de zhōng huá, fù xìng de zhōng huá.
 wǒ ài zhōng huá, wǒ ài zhōng huá, wǒ ài zhōng huá.</lyrics>
<title>zhù fú zhōng huá 迦南867</title>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
